# Do not commit real secrets. Copy this file to .env locally.
#
# This template lists ONLY environment variables actually referenced
# in PRISM source code via `process.env.X`. Generated 2026-05-15.
# Source: PRISM_03_SECRET_AND_ENV_REGISTER.md §6.
#
# Provide your own values locally; .env is ignored by .gitignore.

# === Runtime / general ===
